- Jeannie!
- Jonas!

27:50.252 --> 27:51.284
Hey!

27:51.320 --> 27:52.285
Jonas!

27:52.321 --> 27:53.520
Be careful.

27:53.555 --> 27:55.188
I'm sorry.

27:55.224 --> 27:58.258
Does it still hurt real bad?

27:58.293 --> 27:59.259
I'm okay.

27:59.294 --> 28:01.228
- Hey.
- Hey.

28:03.298 --> 28:05.098
Hi, Daddy.

28:05.134 --> 28:07.701
This is such a nice surprise.

28:07.736 --> 28:10.637
Mama's gonna be so sad she
wasn't here to greet ya.

28:10.672 --> 28:11.771
Where is she?

28:11.807 --> 28:13.707
Out with Uncle Phineas.

28:13.742 --> 28:16.143
Don't worry... Valentina's here.

28:16.178 --> 28:18.515
Well, let's send her home.

28:18.547 --> 28:21.114
