28:30.592 --> 28:33.960
I thought... we were going to bed.

28:33.996 --> 28:36.263
You and I should have a word first.

28:39.034 --> 28:41.935
I don't know what I
can say to you, Charles.

28:41.970 --> 28:43.103
I'm sorry.

28:43.138 --> 28:44.671
"Sorry" don't help Ramon.

28:44.706 --> 28:47.274
Didn't you learn anything at the river?

28:47.309 --> 28:50.323
When the ranch got shot up?
You know how bad things are.

28:50.354 --> 28:53.146
You know better than getting
caught up with Niles Gilbert.

28:53.148 --> 28:55.115
I didn't know what was
gonna happen to Ramon.

28:55.150 --> 28:56.349
I really didn't.

28:56.385 --> 28:57.751
Then you weren't using your head.

28:57.786 --> 28:59.519
I couldn't stop it.

29:13.335 --> 29:15.435
I understand.

29:18.473 --> 29:20.407
I've been there, too.

29:27.349 --> 29:28.315
Hi.

29:28.350 --> 29:30.016
What a nice surprise.

29:30.052 --> 29:31.484
How long you staying?

29:31.520 --> 29:32.986
Were y'all at a party?

29:34.189 --> 29:35.388
Honey, what's wrong?

29:44.044 --> 29:45.611
So, that's it?

29:45.647 --> 29:48.014
He gets off scot-free?

29:48.049 --> 29:49.949
What did you want me to do?

29:49.984 --> 29:52.185
I don't know... Something.

29:52.220 --> 29:54.654
Make him go to church
and do charitable works...

29:54.689 --> 29:56.322
Some kind of penance.

29:58.226 --> 29:59.525
You don't agree?

29:59.561 --> 30:01.827
Sal, he's in agony... I promise you.

30:01.863 --> 30:03.930
Good. He should be.

30:06.434 --> 30:08.968
Don't look at me like that.

30:09.003 --> 30:13.306
He's surrounded by men who
think there's glory in violence.

30:13.341 --> 30:16.209
It's teaching him the wrong things.

30:30.258 --> 30:32.258
That's a gift for your daddy.

30:38.866 --> 30:41.534
I was thinking for his
40th, but I haven't decided.

30:47.375 --> 30:49.408
He can't even look at me.

30:51.212 --> 30:54.213
If that's the case, it's only
because he's seeing himself.

30:57.652 --> 30:58.718
What does that mean?

31:02.290 --> 31:06.125
After Everett and your grandma died,

31:06.160 --> 31:10.196
the Colonel kept your
daddy and me close.

31:10.231 --> 31:13.699
Just took us along
for everything he did.

31:13.735 --> 31:18.437
And we had a few real bad
years with cattle thieves.

31:18.473 --> 31:21.274
And the, uh, Colonel
took it real personal.

31:22.977 --> 31:27.613
Decided to rid the county
of all of its bad apples.

31:27.649 --> 31:31.017
And, of course, we were
there... at his side.

31:32.820 --> 31:34.654
When we caught someone,

31:34.689 --> 31:36.656
we strung a noose around their neck,

31:36.691 --> 31:38.891
sat 'em on a horse.

31:38.926 --> 31:42.061
Your daddy and I would slap
the horse on its backside.

31:44.299 --> 31:46.065
The guy would drop.

31:47.702 --> 31:49.669
Just hang there.

31:52.340 --> 31:57.910
I remember this one
time, tree limb broke...

31:57.945 --> 32:01.047
and the rustler just got dragged
by his neck through the brush.

32:04.285 --> 32:06.385
Your daddy ended up shooting the fella.

32:11.025 --> 32:13.025
He was 12 by then.

32:16.831 --> 32:20.766
I think something's
changed in you, Pete.

32:20.802 --> 32:23.803
And it's something you don't understand.

32:27.542 --> 32:30.843
And you won't let me near
enough to understand it, either.

32:33.381 --> 32:35.232
We can't live like this.

32:40.521 --> 32:42.021
I know.

32:44.992 --> 32:47.493
Look me in the eye, at least.

33:02.910 --> 33:04.410
Sal.

33:07.749 --> 33:09.415
It's fine.

33:12.053 --> 33:13.919
I'm fine.

33:24.932 --> 33:28.901
I never wanted any of this to happen.

33:28.936 --> 33:31.604
I thought everything bad I
went through when we were kids,

33:31.639 --> 33:33.038
all of it was gonna stop with me.

33:33.074 --> 33:36.942
I was... I was gonna
be the end of the line.

33:42.717 --> 33:44.083
I know it's killing you.

33:47.221 --> 33:50.156
But there's nothing I can do, is there?

33:54.228 --> 33:57.396
You're so sad that nobody can reach you.

34:01.936 --> 34:05.571
Are you happy here... In the city?

34:09.310 --> 34:10.810
Yeah.

34:14.282 --> 34:16.782
Then you and the kids should stay.

34:24.759 --> 34:27.659
You know...

34:27.695 --> 34:28.994
